##When I was released from prison, I signed up to fight the epidemic in the county, but I didn't expect...

Micro Signal Xinminzhoukan

Function description, depth and angle —— this is what we can do.

Should you be a selfish person or stick to yourself: BE USEFUL TO SOCIETY?

Oral | high concentration

Sorting out | Shen Lin

Today is my 14th day of voluntary isolation at home, and I'm supposed to be getting out of the house. But recent events have complicated my feelings.

My name is Gao Ji, 20 years old when making friends carelessly, did some wrong to the society, for this, I paid nearly 10 years of youth. In the past 10 years, I have not been exposed to the outside world, and the taste of being behind bars is not very good, but the habits I have developed over the years, especially the strengthening of political education for prisoners since the 18th National Congress, have made me like to pay attention to current affairs, and I like to think.

Last August, I was released from prison. Because too long disjointed with the society, first returned to the home village, help the family to do some farm work, also familiar with this strange world.

Around the time of the New Year, an epidemic broke out.

On the second day of the Lunar New Year, my village was closed to traffic and a return point was set up at the entrance. Soon after, I heard the news that a family in the next town had come back from Wuhan and had been diagnosed with a new case of coronary pneumonia.

Our County is relatively small, there is no special hospital for infectious patients, after the outbreak, the county emergency response, intends to establish a small "small Tangshan" to isolate the confirmed and suspected cases. The site is also several twists and turns, at first chose a half-finished building, renovation can be used, but the local people are very opposed, and then chose a hotel, also because the opposition too big did not succeed. Later, the county decided to build a simple quarantine zone on a wide stretch of land along the road leading to the infected area. In order to make time, the construction site is the kind of simple board room.

After the location was determined, however, there were difficulties in recruiting workers. Because is builds the house in the epidemic area, the local populace needs in the home isolation, outside village's nobody is willing to go, feared is infected. By chance, I saw this information, I think, finally can do something useful to society.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Construction site

I am not how selfless, this disease so severe and no medicine, how can not be afraid of it?

I thought long and hard before I went: First of all, the isolation point is to do simple board housing, for the technical requirements are not high, pure manual labor, I can help; the second government led to do this project, i'm sure we'll have safeguards in place, life is guaranteed, and third, when I was in prison, I was thinking, as ordinary people, how many times in our lives do we get to do something about the damage we've done to society?

I told some of my friends that I wanted to help out at the site, but most of them turned me down. Later, I persuaded my younger brother (Gao Qiu) and a junior high school classmate (Wang Liu Qing) to come with me. They are bricklayers, still skilled workers, should be able to help.

Before we left, the villagers began to oppose us. The reason was simple. We went to the epidemic area to build a quarantine point. They were afraid that we would get sick and the whole village would be affected, "Even if that town has more patients, it's none of your business. What are you going to do? " "Aren't you sticking your nose where it doesn't belong? " "You'll be causing trouble in the village! ".

To tell the truth, I understand the villagers'thinking, but if you don't do it, I don't do it, the quarantine point can not be built, the disease will spread, and eventually it will spread to more people as if the situation in Wuhan is so serious, compared with the brothers from all over who gave their lives to build mount thor and Mount Vulcan, what is the situation here?

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
The staff disinfected us

I think doing this is conscious, it's noble. I did not listen to the opposition, or with the county, the county sent a car to pick us up, the village can not stop us. Early on the morning of February 11th, we arrived at the quarantine site, where a group of people were already working.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Simple isolation point

To the site, the person in charge of us to do a simple safety training, to explain some matters needing attention. It was a bit rainy that two days, we put on the simple protective clothing formally on duty.

In fact, the work site is not difficult, but to move things, decorate the plumbing, cleaning and sanitation. After 36 hours of work, the barrier was built. The county government gave each of us a certificate that we had no contact with people in the affected areas, so we didn't have to go home and be quarantined for 14 days.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Late night rush

We went back to the village in the middle of the night on February 12, and when we woke up the next morning, the villagers knew we were back, and the reaction was huge: someone reported the situation to the Party secretary, someone called the police, and the last party secretary, who had retired, ... And called the county to report us...

Soon, the current party secretary and some village cadres came to our house, told us that the villagers have a great response, meaning that my brother and I temporarily moved to the village near the Highway Junction under the bridge isolated; He also criticized our behavior, saying we were overreaching and giving him a hard time.

I showed them the certificate the government had given us, and the Party secretary was a little softer, he said. I can't say if you have the certificate, but the people in the village have a lot of opinions. You should stay at home for a while.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
After the village party secretary left, I was quite depressed. I think, I clearly did a right thing, do not ask for the big red flower certificate, but why will get such a reaction? Especially the former village party secretary called me, I was so surprised, I think he an old cadre, consciousness should be above me, why not support me?

I was also told that it was because my mind was out of sync with my surroundings, like a city dweller wearing a rolex in the country. What difference could a village person make? It's like a Shanghai Watch. I thought and thought, maybe so, the fear of the unknown in the village made me and my brother the "unlucky people" in the village, plus the food was in the field, the grain was in the rice bowl, and it was no big deal not to go out for 14 days, for the sake of the villagers'peace of mind, I'll volunteer for a 14-day quarantine.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
After work, my junior high classmates sent me a friend circle

But those days of gossip listen to my heart is still very hard, and some people say that my brother and I to help the government but the government is isolated, really silly cloud.

One day, my brother's kids went out to play, and they were having fun with the kids in the neighborhood. Did Not expect someone to call the village soon to go, the village cadres soon came to deal with. In fact, the villagers near my home have also been "spurned" , neighbors want to go to the other side of the village door-to-door, the villagers always drive back there.

Last week, a lot of places went back to work. Village people have been out to work, open health card, my brother and I also want to get a, but did not walk a few steps, but was the village party secretary ordered delay. Because of these things, my mother also began to blame me, I had a great opinion, think I slowed down the family to go out to work to earn money rhythm.

When I came out of prison, I told myself that I wanted to change, and that change had to come through action, and give back to society. But these days, I can't help but wonder, am I doing the right thing or the wrong thing? Should you be a selfish person or stick to yourself: BE USEFUL TO SOCIETY?

My Quarantine's over, but my questions are getting deeper.

Image Credit: Gaoji
